Package com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.sort.helper

Class InstrumenterDummy

java.lang.Object
com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.sort.helper.InstrumenterDummy
All Implemented Interfaces:
Instrument
public class InstrumenterDummy extends Object implements Instrument
A dummy implementation of the Instrument interface, primarily used for testing or as a placeholder when no instrumentation is needed. This implementation does not perform any meaningful actions or record any statistics.
